quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,7,"By the heaven with its numerous forms:"{1},footnotes:1:1
  51,8,"surely you are at variance (about the Hereafter);"{1},footnotes:1:1
  51,9,"though only those who are averse to the Truth will turn away from (believing in it)."{1},footnotes:1:1
  51,10,"Doomed are the conjecturers"{1},footnotes:1:1